{"data":[{"date":"08:01 07/08","title":"Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sao Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/guardiola-xac-nhan-se-de-stones-da-tien-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y trong m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh Community Shield v\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00f4m ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Stones s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola, John Stones c\u0169ng n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t gia nh\u1eadp Man City m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi trong vai tr\u00f2 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 thi tho\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield v\u1edbi Chelsea m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Stones \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn khi Vincent Kompany v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p Aymeric Laporte r\u1ed3i sau l\u00e0 Nicolas Otamendi th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/guardiola-xac-nhan-se-de-stones-da-tien-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Stones \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c cu\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u201cStones \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong 10 t\u1edbi 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Stones c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u1ede Premier League c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng chung s\u1ee9c.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nStones c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kompany hay Otamendi \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd c\u00f9ng Laporte s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh 2 t\u1edbi 3 su\u1ea5t \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man City. V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, Guardiola n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/HLV-Pep-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Guardiola x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Stones \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cStones bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao b\u1edfi Kompany v\u00e0 Otamendi c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng 1 (22h ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt 12/8).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-thu-choi-an-tuong-va-te-nhat-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-172-193815.html\">3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-ngay-el-kun-nhay-mua-duoi-anh-mat-troi-172-193813.html\">G\u00f3c Man City: Khi El Kun nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-khien-chelsea-that-tran-truoc-man-city-172-193811.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-172-193809.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-pep-team-bao-tin-du-cho-nuoc-anh-172-193808.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: \u201cPep team\u201d b\u00e1o tin d\u1eef cho n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2083","checkdouble":"193904"},{"date":"07:23 07/08","title":"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-giai-u16-dna-hlv-dt-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, ch\u00ednh l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u00ea ch\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1, HLV \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/22/Tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-giai-U16-DNA,-HLV-DT-U16-Viet-Nam-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U16 Myanmar</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 6/8, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Myanmar. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i so thua k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh Myanmar v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV Myanmar \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen x\u00e3 giao cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam may m\u1eafn n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Malaysia v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68-372-193846.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u16-viet-nam-vs-u16-myanmar-ngay-hom-nay-68-372-193846.html\">U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U16 Myanmar (KT): U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Myanmar v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nVideo: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U16 Myanmar<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/U16-Viet-Nam-2-2-U16-Myanmar.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2082","checkdouble":"193905"},{"date":"07:40 07/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/nong-paul-pogba-dat-thoa-thuan-voi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</h2><h2>Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf th\u1eeba. Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a n\u00e0y g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Marcus Rashford th\u1eeba k\u1ebf s\u1ed1 \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 v\u1ed1n v\u00f4 ch\u1ee7 thay cho s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ly do Marcus Rashford mang ao so 10 cua Man Utd duoc Mourinho tiet lo.\" title=\"L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 10 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111eo tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng David Beckham (m\u00f9a 1996-97 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n sang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7), Teddy Sheringham, Ruud Van Nistelrooy hay g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Wayne Rooney. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1edfi Rashford m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 c\u00f3 52 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y: &quot;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Rashford lu\u00f4n d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Wayne Rooney&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec Zlatan Ibrahimovic l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean Rashford ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1i, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u00ec s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang tr\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man Utd theo l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man Utd s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Marcus Rashford:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rashford-va-chiec-ao-huyen-thoai-trach-nhiem-nang-ne-kha-nang-han-che-172-193843.html\">Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\">N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-tru-cot-cat-giam-ky-nghi-tap-trung-som-cung-mu-172-192478.html\">3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup-172-192455.html\">B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho-172-192306.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong &ldquo;danh s\u00e1ch \u0111en&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2081","checkdouble":"193906"},{"date":"07:43 07/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 07/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0708-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-mu.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 07/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0708 Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0708 Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/tua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuanzebe c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Aston Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trung v\u1ec7 Axel Tuanzebe r\u1eddi M.U t\u1edbi Aston Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edf ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca g\u1eedi MU: 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng + Mina + Andre Gomes = Pogba?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng trung v\u1ec7 Mina v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1eb1ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kroos: &ldquo;Qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, Real Madrid s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wolvehampton muon mua Vida\" title=\"Wolvehampton mu\u1ed1n mua Vida\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-muon-gianh-hang-hot-world-cup-voi-arsenal-va-liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Vida</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid thay Thibaut Courtois, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ed1t 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Paul Pogba chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, theo Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AC Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong khi Hazard,&nbsp;Giroud v\u00e0 Kante \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ttcn-tai-anh-dong-cua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Toby Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Tottenham mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid nh\u1eafm sao Juventus thay th\u1ebf Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2080","checkdouble":"193907"},{"date":"07:47 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Fenerbahce 02h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-benfica-vs-fenerbahce-02h00-ngay-88-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Benfica vs Fenerbahce l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Fenerbahce 02h00 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Fenerbahce 02h00 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Benfica-vs-Fenerbahce.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Benfica vs Fenerbahce</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Benfica vs Fenerbahce: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Fenerbahce tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Fenerbahce \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 7 t\u00e2n binh, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Ayew t\u1eeb CLB\u00a0Swansea. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phillip Cocu \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 (ch\u1ec9 thua 1/6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u00eam nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Benfica, Fenerbahce v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.\u00a0Th\u1ef1c ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Champions League l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008-09. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Fenerbahce, Benfica li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League \u1edf 7 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft (m\u00f9a 2011-12 v\u00e0 2015-16).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tay Porto n\u00ean Benfica \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n t\u1edbi 11 t\u00e2n binh. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Rui Vit\u00f3ria g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Dortmund v\u00e0 Juventus (trong 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c) \u1edf ICC 2018. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon, Benfica kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00ean Benfica ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00eam nay h\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o \u01b0u th\u1ebf c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Rui Vit\u00f3ria c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi 10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 8. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00eam nay h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1edfi Fenerbahce v\u00e0 Benfica \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. 12/14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Benfica \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2 b\u00e0n \u1edf 8/10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede Europa League m\u00f9a 2012-13, Fenerbahce \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Benfica 1-0 \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Benfica (4-1-4-1): Varela - Almeida, Conti, R.Dias, Grimaldo - Fejsa - Salvio, Zivkovic, Felix, Cervi - Jonas.<br>\r\n+ Fenerbahce (4-4-2): Demirel - Ozbayrakli, Neustadter, Guveli, Kaldirim - Potuk, Topal, Tufan, Valbuena - Soldado, Elmas.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2079","checkdouble":"193908"},{"date":"08:15 07/08","title":"Mourinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</h2><h2>Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf th\u1eeba. Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a n\u00e0y g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Marcus Rashford th\u1eeba k\u1ebf s\u1ed1 \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 v\u1ed1n v\u00f4 ch\u1ee7 thay cho s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ly do Marcus Rashford mang ao so 10 cua Man Utd duoc Mourinho tiet lo.\" title=\"L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/mourinho-giai-thich-ly-do-marcus-rashford-mang-ao-so-10-cua-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 10 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf Old Trafford \u0111eo tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng David Beckham (m\u00f9a 1996-97 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n sang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7), Teddy Sheringham, Ruud Van Nistelrooy hay g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Wayne Rooney. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1edfi Rashford m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 c\u00f3 52 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Marcus Rashford mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y: &quot;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Rashford lu\u00f4n d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Wayne Rooney&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec Zlatan Ibrahimovic l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean Rashford ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1i, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u00ec s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang tr\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man Utd theo l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man Utd s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Marcus Rashford:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rashford-va-chiec-ao-huyen-thoai-trach-nhiem-nang-ne-kha-nang-han-che-172-193843.html\">Rashford v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\">N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-tru-cot-cat-giam-ky-nghi-tap-trung-som-cung-mu-172-192478.html\">3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup-172-192455.html\">B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho-172-192306.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong &ldquo;danh s\u00e1ch \u0111en&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2078","checkdouble":"193910"},{"date":"08:04 07/08","title":"HLV Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/hlv-uzbekistan-noi-gi-truoc-tran-tai-dau-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Nuraliev Dilshod c\u1ee7a Uzbekistan th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a BTC v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i bao g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn U23 Uzbekistan b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/thua-palestine-hlv-u23-uzbekistan-thua-nhan-thua-kem-u23-viet-nam.jpg\"><br>\r\n            <em>HLV U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Uzbekistan c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 n\u00e0y th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng m\u00e0 th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i U.23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1eb7n d\u00f2 k\u1ef9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c xa c\u00e1i ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn 120 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong d\u00e1nh s\u00e1ch 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 HLV Nuraliev Dilshod mang sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng U.23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 HLV Nuraliev cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng U.23 Uzbekistan sang \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U.23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG n\u00ean r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3u nhau, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i&rdquo;, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n U.23 Uzbekistan t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19g30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/8. Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 07/8): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2077","checkdouble":"193911"},{"date":"08:24 07/08","title":"\u201cSao x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/barkley-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ross Barkley ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u201cl\u1ed9t x\u00e1c\u201d d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri sau nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua trong 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, Chelsea chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i n\u1eeda n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Ross Barkley v\u1edbi Everton. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho The Blues. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 4 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Maurizio Sarri. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi, Barkley b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. D\u00f9 Chelsea thua Man City 0-2 t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ross Barkley ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/barkley-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barkley ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0 khi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau, Barkley mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. &ldquo;V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1edbi Man City, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i&rdquo;, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n vui v\u1ebb ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd cho HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i mong mu\u1ed1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tin ch\u1eafc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khung-khiep-chelsea-chi-89-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-courtois-172-193897.html\">Kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp: Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-courtois-va-hazard-cu-thoai-mai-ra-di-172-193879.html\">Sao Chelsea: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-172-193870.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey-172-193859.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2076","checkdouble":"193912"},{"date":"08:39 07/08","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/ac-milan-khuoc-tu-loi-de-nghi-cua-arsenal-cho-ricardo-rodriguez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u00e0nh cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ricardo Rodriguez.</h2><h2>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Milan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Sead Kolasinac s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 10 tu\u1ea7n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNacho Monreal c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City ngay trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u00e0n Premier League. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Emery ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Ainsley Maitland-Niles.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milan kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ricardo Rodriguez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Milan kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ricardo Rodriguez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/ac-milan-khuoc-tu-loi-de-nghi-cua-arsenal-cho-ricardo-rodriguez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 Rodriguez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Corriere dello Sport, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-thuy-sy-thay-nacho-monreal-172-193853.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Ricardo Rodriguez</span> c\u1ee7a AC Milan. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milano \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Rodriguez r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n San Siro. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Arsenal c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1edbm h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Man United thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi Leicester t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<h2>Milan quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Rodriguez</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Arsenal chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c AC Milan nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 Rossoneri c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n chia tay tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0128 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 g\u1eedi th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn th\u00eam tin bu\u1ed3n. B\u1edfi ph\u00eda Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i top 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRicardo Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n San Siro t\u1eeb Wolfsburg m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 47 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng Rodriguez v\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c fan b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-laurent-koscielny-172-193898.html\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2075","checkdouble":"193914"},{"date":"08:49 07/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea cho Nantes m\u01b0\u1ee3n Matt Miazga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 2 m\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb The Blues.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Miazga kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMatt Miazga gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb New York Red Bulls v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. L\u00fac m\u1edbi t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh khi tranh ch\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111i, Miazga kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c HLV Chelsea. N\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2015/16, khi The Blues kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, trung v\u1ec7 cao 1m93 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea cho Nantes m\u01b0\u1ee3n Matt Miazga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea cho Nantes m\u01b0\u1ee3n Matt Miazga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-cho-Nantes-muon-Matt-Miazga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Miazga ch\u01a1i cho Vitesse 2 m\u00f9a qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 2 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, Miazga \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Vitesse Arnhem. Sau khi Antonio Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i, t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Maurizio Sarri v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng 7 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sang ch\u01a1i cho Nantes</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 m\u00f9a qua, Miazga \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Vitesse. Anh g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Europa League trong c\u1ea3 2 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f3. S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Matt Miazga\" title=\"hau ve Matt Miazga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea cho Nantes m\u01b0\u1ee3n Matt Miazga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Miazga chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i cho Nantes t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;Chim ho\u00e0ng y\u1ebfn&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Caen \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean New York Red Bulls.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMiazga tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M\u1ef9 th\u1ee9 2 gia nh\u1eadp Nantes sau Alejandro Bedoya, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i 96 tr\u1eadn cho CLB n\u00e0y tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong 3 n\u0103m t\u1eeb 2013 t\u1edbi 2016. Nantes s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Monaco t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ligue 1 th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-courtois-va-hazard-cu-thoai-mai-ra-di-172-193879.html\">Sao Chelsea: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-172-193870.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey-172-193859.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/olivier-giroud-khong-roi-chelsea-toi-marseille-172-193783.html\">B\u1ecb h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i, Giroud v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2074","checkdouble":"193916"},{"date":"22:25 06/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/nhung-diem-tich-cuc-va-han-che-cua-mu-sau-tran-thua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c khi ch\u1ec9 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bayern trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Nhung-diem-tich-cuc-va-han-che-cua-MU-sau-tran-thua-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Darmian t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u00e9m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Franck Ribery v\u00e0 Arjen Robben c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 69. Nh\u01b0ng hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n g\u00ec khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb sung m\u00e3n b\u00ean ph\u00eda Man United l\u00e0 Darmian v\u00e0 Shaw.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Robben v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Premier League, Man United ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a MU c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 trong tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac Man United ph\u1ea3i lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i khi mang v\u1ec1 Kyle Walker v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn gi\u00fap Man xanh c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bailly v\u00e0 Lindelof g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bailly\" title=\"Bailly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/221913-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bailly v\u1eefng nh\u01b0 b\u00e0n th\u1ea1ch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Man United. Trong 416 ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Lindelof c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United, anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f9ng Bailly \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Smalling.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz Arena. Kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Lewandowski. B\u1edfi Bailly \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Lewandowski \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Thomas Muller c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb tay Smalling v\u00e0 Jones. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toby Alderweireld th\u00ec c\u1eb7p Bailly &ndash; Lindelof n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford\" title=\"Rashford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/221922-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Rashford th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u1edf m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi Mata v\u00e0 Sanchez \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193818.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern vs MU</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Hummels v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man United kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Rashford. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng MU v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u00e1o huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Old Trafford tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho Woodward</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CEO Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a MU l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Ed Woodward c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 b\u1ec1 sa th\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch k\u00e9m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f3 HLV n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Premier League hay Champions League v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nguy-khon-mourinho-gui-loi-cau-cuu-hoc-tro-172-193830.html\">M.U nguy kh\u1ed1n, Mourinho g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-10-mu-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193818.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 1-0 MU (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2073","checkdouble":"193883"},{"date":"22:33 06/08","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u2013 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nH\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Oman v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0, b\u1eb1ng si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;t\u00e2n binh&rdquo; \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 sau l\u01b0ng, c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 Olympic, Mr. Park bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i 1 trong 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean qu\u00e1 23 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec1u ra qu\u00e2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/hung.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0o. D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0110T v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u00f4i. V\u0103n L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00f4i trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. C\u00f2n danh s\u00e1ch cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u1ed3m 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1edfi BHL y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y Park: &ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ASIAD.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich-168-193812.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich-168-193812.html\">L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam-168-193810.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam-168-193810.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2072","checkdouble":"193884"},{"date":"06:06 07/08","title":"Willian nh\u1eafn Mourinho: \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/5/28/Willian-tu-choi-kheo-loi-moi-toi-MU-cua-thay-cu-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong khi Hazard, Giroud v\u00e0 Kante \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Man City, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man xanh, The Blues \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Thibaut-Courtois-muon-roi-Chelsea-toi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng Chelsea nh\u01b0ng Courtois th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf Cobham, nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 N'Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018. B\u1ed9 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t vui v\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Theo t\u1edd Telegraph, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-cau-xin-chelsea-hay-buong-tha-cho-courtois-172-193720.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois</span>, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea7u xin Chelsea bu\u00f4ng tha cho th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng Chelsea l\u1ea1i ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Courtois c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real Madrid thi \u0111\u1ea5u, song ph\u00eda Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJan Oblak v\u00e0 Jack Butland \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 hai trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Oblak v\u00e0 Atletico c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Stoke \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Butland.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2071","checkdouble":"193889"},{"date":"06:39 07/08","title":"Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/real-madrid-chot-70-trieu-euro-cho-nguoi-thay-the-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric Real\" title=\"Modric Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/10/13/Deco-Chi-1-cau-thu-Real-du-trinh-khoac-ao-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33 anh v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn M.U, Chelsea hay Inter Milan. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, Inter l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Modric, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 750 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Inter Milan g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Miralem Pjanic thay Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Miralem-Pjanic-thay-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real nh\u1eafm Pjanic thay Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t\u00a0c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Pjanic ho\u00e0n t\u00f2an c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Modric \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, song thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Higuain, Juventus quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pjanic. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1ea3 Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pjanic, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mua Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham</span>, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2070","checkdouble":"193890"},{"date":"05:37 07/08","title":"C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/cuc-nong-mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Tottenham mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 thay th\u1ebf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca, M.U \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/cuc-nong-mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Goal, MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 Spurs \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Tottenham mu\u1ed1n 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n M.U ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 theo ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Goal, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Alderweireld kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Tottenham, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Spurs v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. HLV Pochettino kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Tottenham t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi m\u00e0 Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00ec Tottenham bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn M.U ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu...</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham m\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n Alderweireld cho M.U, song h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n Spurs \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Atletico.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Lascelles\" title=\"hau ve Lascelles\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/leicester-hoi-mua-lascelles-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham nh\u1eafm Lascelles thay Alderweireld\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJamaal Lascelles c\u1ee7a Newcastle v\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tottenham nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alderweireld v\u1edbi Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 12 th\u00e1ng, ng\u00f4i\u00a0sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019, M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alderweireld, song Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u h\u01a1n. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng mua th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU \u0111\u1ec3 Axel Tuanzebe t\u1edbi Aston Villa </span>theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2069","checkdouble":"193891"}]}